attributionInfo.agentName: Jennie & Eddie Luxury Living Boston Team

description: Fort Point Place is a gorgeous loft elevator building converted to condos in 2000 & nestled in the vibrant Fort Point Channel Landmark District, close to excellent restaurants & coffee shops. Enter this beautiful completely renovated top-floor unit through a lovely front foyer, then walk into the living room/kitchen/dining room, complete with expansive open concept space, soaring ceilings, rich maple floors & large windows that allow in an abundance of light all day. The main room boasts an entire wall of exposed brick & oversized wooden beams running across the ceiling. The brand-new kitchen features an island perfect for bar stools & casual eating, stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, & ample storage space. The luxurious bathroom is recently renovated with abundant storage & large glass-enclosed tiled shower. The spacious bedroom easily accommodates a king-sized bed and is adjacent to a massive walk-in closet: one tandem garage space, stacked washer, and dryer.
